      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Well-used but still a capable runner with a strong motor, dependable drivetrain, and plenty of life left for someone who wants an affordable daily, backup car, or project platform. Cosmetic wear and age are present, but the car has the kind of honest mechanical character enthusiasts appreciate: it starts, moves out well, and delivers a straightforward, usable driving experience. A great chance to get into a practical vehicle at a budget-friendly price without paying for showroom looks.",
